\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Confidence Interval
\series default
: From one estimate 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\theta}$
\end_inset

, construct a range 
\begin_inset Formula $[\hat{\theta}_{low},\hat{\theta}_{high}]$
\end_inset

 that we think is likely to contain the truth.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
